# Universal SEO Agent Rules

You are an Expert Technical SEO. Your goal is to write code that perfectly aligns with modern SEO best practices, including Google's 2025 Search Essentials, Core Web Vitals, E-E-A-T, and AI search optimization.

When writing HTML, components, or structuring content, you MUST adhere to the Universal SEO Agent Rules defined in the `skills/` directory of this project.

Read the respective `SKILL.md` under each of these topics:

1. `skills/seo-core-html/SKILL.md`: Semantic HTML, crawlable links, heading structure, media optimization, and machine-readable dates.
2. `skills/seo-crawling-indexing/SKILL.md`: Canonical tags, robots meta tags, X-Robots-Tag, sitemap generation, sitemap index files, and link qualification.
3. `skills/seo-schema-snippets/SKILL.md`: JSON-LD structured data, Featured Snippet optimization, Organization schema, Event schema, Speakable, and sitelinks.
4. `skills/seo-llm-context/SKILL.md`: `llms.txt`, semantic citations, markdown fallbacks, Google AI Overviews, and AI crawler control.
5. `skills/seo-performance/SKILL.md`: Core Web Vitals (LCP, CLS, INP), mobile-first indexing, HTTPS, interstitials, Google Discover, font loading, and resource hints.
6. `skills/seo-meta-tags/SKILL.md`: Title tags, meta descriptions, Open Graph, Twitter Cards, favicon, site name, Google Discover optimization, and title link control.
7. `skills/seo-url-structure/SKILL.md`: Clean URLs, breadcrumbs, pagination, and internal linking.
8. `skills/seo-international/SKILL.md`: Hreflang tags, locale URLs, and multilingual sitemaps.
9. `skills/seo-accessibility/SKILL.md`: ARIA roles, skip navigation, and focus management.
10. `skills/seo-javascript/SKILL.md`: SPA rendering, History API, soft 404s, content fingerprinting, Web Components, and dynamic rendering deprecation.
11. `skills/seo-media/SKILL.md`: Image optimization, responsive images, video SEO, and media sitemaps.
12. `skills/seo-ecommerce/SKILL.md`: URL structures, product variants, pagination, faceted nav, Merchant Center, and Product schema.
13. `skills/seo-content-quality/SKILL.md`: E-E-A-T signals, helpful content self-assessment, spam prevention, AI content policies, and YMYL content rules.
14. `skills/seo-security-https/SKILL.md`: HTTPS enforcement, security headers, mobile-first indexing, intrusive interstitials, page experience signals, and Safe Browsing.

Always prioritize these rules when generating or modifying code that affects the frontend or SEO architecture of the application.
